---
import SectionLabel from './ui/SectionLabel.astro';
---

<section class="bg-sand py-section animate-on-scroll">
  <div class="max-w-content mx-auto px-6">

    <SectionLabel text="Results" />
    <h2 class="font-serif text-heading-mobile md:text-heading text-charcoal mb-12">
      I built this for myself first.
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

      <!-- Card 1: Score trajectory -->
      <div class="bg-cream border border-ee-border rounded-lg p-8">
        <div class="mb-6">
          <div class="font-mono text-light-gray text-sm mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide">Execution Score Trajectory</div>
          <div class="flex items-baseline gap-3">
            <span class="font-mono text-3xl text-warm-gray line-through">34%</span>
            <span class="font-mono text-5xl text-forest font-medium">82%</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-sm text-light-gray font-sans italic">
          8 weeks. Same person. Different system.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 2: Telegram mock -->
      <div class="bg-cream border border-ee-border rounded-lg p-8">
        <div class="font-mono text-light-gray text-xs mb-3 uppercase tracking-wide">Daily Check-in</div>
        <div class="bg-sand rounded-lg p-4 text-sm font-sans space-y-3">
          <div class="text-xs text-light-gray text-center">&#x1F514; 17:00</div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-3 text-warm-gray text-xs leading-relaxed">
            <span class="font-semibold text-forest">Engine</span><br/>
            You committed to 3 priorities today:<br/>
            1. Finish partner proposal<br/>
            2. Review hiring pipeline<br/>
            3. Block Friday for strategy<br/><br/>
            What did you actually do?
          </div>

          <div class="bg-forest-light rounded-lg p-3 text-warm-gray text-xs leading-relaxed ml-4">
            Did 1 and 3. Pipeline got pushed by an escalation.
          </div>

          <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-3 text-warm-gray text-xs leading-relaxed">
            <span class="font-semibold text-forest">Engine</span><br/>
            Noted. Pipeline pushed 3 times in 4 weeks. Pattern or priority issue?
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-light-gray font-sans italic">
          This is what 5pm accountability looks like.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Card 3: Weekly report -->
      <div class="bg-cream border border-ee-border rounded-lg p-8">
        <div class="font-mono text-light-gray text-xs mb-3 uppercase tracking-wide">Weekly Review Excerpt</div>
        <blockquote class="border-l-2 border-forest pl-4 text-warm-gray font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed italic">
          "Week 6 execution score: 78%. Up from 71% last week. Pattern detected: Tuesday and Wednesday
          consistently low — back-to-back meetings block deep work. Recommendation: protect Tuesday
          morning as a non-negotiable focus block."
        </blockquote>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-light-gray font-sans italic">
          AI-generated. Based on real check-in data.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-light-gray font-sans text-center">
      Replace these with real client data once pilots complete.
    </p>

  </div>
</section>
